00:52:20.000 --> 00:52:21.000
Yes.

00:52:21.000 --> 00:52:35.000
There's a local historian that Mark Lewis knows about who has found some links in the documents with a Flemish family who held Whitsun.

00:52:35.000 --> 00:52:37.000
How curious.

00:52:37.000 --> 00:52:41.000
It's one of the exciting things about being an academic.

00:52:41.000 --> 00:52:42.000
Yes.

00:52:42.000 --> 00:52:50.000
