00:54:44.000 --> 00:54:56.000
I think if there had been a positive from the M4 diversion, it might have drawn a line on the map that the planners could have said, no more.

00:54:56.000 --> 00:55:01.000
I'm not developing south of that line.

00:55:01.000 --> 00:55:07.000
I had this discussion with various people about the pros and cons of that motorway.

00:55:07.000 --> 00:55:11.000
It would have taken some land from the levels.

00:55:12.000 --> 00:55:19.000
